Package: lbmech
Type: Package
Title: A Package to Study the Mechanics of Landscape and Behavior
Version: 0.5.1
Author: Andres G. Mejia Ramon
Maintainer: Andres G. Mejia Ramon <andres.mejiaramon@oist.jp>
Description: A series of functions to calculate the cost required to move across the landscape in terms of (1) time, (2) mechanical work, and (3) net metabolic expenditure---energy, as well as (4) estimate local indicators of dispersion. 
